eNarrative.eNarrative.01: Car was T-boned from the right while heading north. Pt was sitting in the most severely impacted part of the car. Injury to neck caused respiratory arrest, followed by cardiac arrest, before we arrived. We performed RSI and transported. Pulse returned enroute.
